OL,6,FA landowner has been fined thousands
OL,7,Fof pounds for illegally dumping and
OL,8,Fburning waste near Maidstone.
OL,10,FMr Langley Beck owns the Bell Lane
OL,11,Fsite which stretches across a
OL,12,Fsignificant area of more than 36 acres
OL,13,Fin the North Kent Downs National
OL,14,FLandscape - formally an area of
OL,15,Foutstanding national beauty.
OL,17,FMr Beck has littered the site with
OL,18,Fcommercial and industrial waste for
OL,19,Fthe past 19 years leaving the land
OL,20,Fcontaminated.
