OL,6,FOver the years, Maidstone Borough
OL,7,FCouncil (MBC) has been trying to
OL,8,Fresolve the issue.
OL,10,FTony Harwood, MBC Cabinet Member for
OL,11,FPlanning Policy and Management, said:
OL,12,F"The Council has worked hard in trying
OL,13,Fto stop the catastrophic harm being
OL,14,Finflicted on this ancient woodland
OL,15,Fsite and ensure a clean-up with the
OL,16,Flandowner - over many years, however
OL,17,Fhe chose to ignore an Enforcement
OL,18,FNotice and then a Full Injunction.
