OL,6,F"Although this has been a long,
OL,7,Fcomplex and extremely difficult case,
OL,8,Fthe outcome is appropriate and sends
OL,9,Fout a strong message that Maidstone
OL,10,FBorough Council will not tolerate
OL,11,Fabuse of our precious countryside.
OL,13,F"This sentence now brings these
OL,14,Fparticular criminal proceedings to a
OL,15,Fclose, but we vow to be just as tough
OL,16,Fwith those other offenders we are
OL,17,Factively enforcing against."
