OL,3,CLandowner fined thousands of pounds
OL,4,Cfor illegally dumping and burning waste
OL,6,FMaidstone County Court fined Mr Beck
OL,7,F#60,000, awarded costs to the council
OL,8,Fof #40,000 and a victim surcharge of
OL,9,F#170. Mr Beck was given 12 months to
OL,10,Fpay the costs and will serve 16 months
OL,11,Fin prison if he fails to do so.
OL,13,FMr Beck's suspended prison sentence
OL,14,Fsays he needs to stop living on the
OL,15,Fland and clear it up within 18 months.
OL,17,FIf he doesn't, he could go to prison.
